facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ["During the cast reunion with Janet Hubert, Alfonso Ribeiro is nowhere to be seen. Ribeiro and Hubert have been at odds over the years, with very public rows: he spoke ill of her in a 2011 video and she bashed a 2017 picture of him, among other instances.
